description:
Googly in his pumpkin-themed suit and the menacing Jack Clipper have arrived!

This DLC contains:
• Googly (Formal) *1
• Jack Clipper *2
*1 After the DLC has been installed, players with a Human Rank of B- or higher can obtain Googly (Formal) from a stamp card.
*2 After installing the DLC, players with a Monster Rank of A- or higher can purchase Jack Clipper in the shop.
name: 40,000+ Downloads Milestone DLC
